source.name: Supplemental Nutrition Assistance Program (SNAP) Data System
source.description: This data set provides time-series data on State and county-level estimates of Supplemental Nutrition Assistance Program (SNAP) participation and benefit levels, combined with area estimates of total population, the number of persons in poverty, and selected socio-demographic characteristics of the population. Data are presented in an interactive map and are also available for download.
